{"type":"message","id":"f26ef382","parentId":"c470ad17","timestamp":"2026-03-29T23:22:08.645Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-30 00:01:48 GMT+8] Exec completed (tidal-br, code 0) :: y! To view your project's live URL. EDGEONE_DEPLOY_URL=https://mingox-dzlbtybw.edgeone.cool?eo_token=2b3cacdf22fbb6a089130b2eb9100253&eo_time=1774800108 EDGEONE_DEPLOY_TYPE=preset…\nSystem: [2026-03-30 07:22:08 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 申广亮 (ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb) [msg:om_x100b53af0f3998a4c4a57ae4ea67a73]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53af0f3998a4c4a57ae4ea67a73\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb\",\n  \"sender\": \"申广亮\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-30 07:22 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"申广亮 (ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb\",\n  \"name\": \"申广亮\"\n}\n```\n\nMx deploy"}],"timestamp":1774826528643}}
{"type":"message","id":"b682c959","parentId":"f26ef382","timestamp":"2026-03-29T23:22:12.528Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has sent a message \"Mx deploy\" which seems to be requesting help with deploying something, possibly related to the EdgeOne deployment shown in the system message.\n\nLet me check what I should do first:\n\n1. Read SOUL.md - this is who I am\n2. Read USER.md - this is who I'm helping  \n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md for today and yesterday\n4. Since this is a main session (direct chat), also read MEMORY.md\n\nLet me start by reading these files to understand the context better.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"I'll help you with deploying. Let me first read my core files to understand the context."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3be7aad3915b011dcb2684c25bba","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/SOUL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3be7ab7cfb3b8840c97b1f1c2fef","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/USER.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3be7ac0fc0b766b8c015bb4fb2a7","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/MEMORY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3be7acb8f8d938d8e74b130fb5d9","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/2026-03-30.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3be7ada0f4f3be72bb044c418343","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/2026-03-29.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":5021,"output":333,"cacheRead":34176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39530,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774826528644}}
{"type":"message","id":"c41bfa4f","parentId":"b682c959","timestamp":"2026-03-29T23:22:12.572Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d3be7aad3915b011dcb2684c25bba","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774826532568}}
{"type":"message","id":"1034dee1","parentId":"c41bfa4f","timestamp":"2026-03-29T23:22:12.576Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d3be7ab7cfb3b8840c97b1f1c2fef","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774826532572}}
