{"type":"message","id":"ce782147","parentId":"fc214151","timestamp":"2026-03-29T23:22:12.590Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d3be7ada0f4f3be72bb044c418343","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-29\n\n## MingoX 项目进展\n\n### MX 指令执行流程\n1. 接收 MX 指令 + URL 或图片\n2. 拉取仓库最新代码\n3. 处理内容并生成双语文章（格式：posts/YYYY-MM-DD-title.html）\n4. 更新首页 index.html\n5. 提交 Git 并推送到 Gitee\n6. 部署到 EdgeOne Pages\n\n### 部署状态\n- Gitee Pages: https://siglea.gitee.io/news\n- EdgeOne Pages: https://mingox-dzlbtybw.edgeone.cool?eo_token=（动态）\n- 项目 ID: pages-7lqkihc9fgyl\n- 令牌已持久化到 ~/.config/edgeone/config.json 和 ~/.git-credentials\n\n### 新增文章\n- 2026-03-29-ai-creation-golden-rules.html - AI创作黄金10条\n\n## 技术问题解决\n\n### 飞书文档访问限制\n- Coze Web Fetch 无法直接访问飞书云文档（my.feishu.cn）\n- 即使设置为\"任何人可查看\"，也只返回标题和摘要，无法获取完整正文\n- 解决方案：使用图片识别工具提取文字内容，或要求用户直接复制粘贴\n\n### 图片识别成功案例\n- 用户发送飞书文档截图\n- 使用 image 工具成功提取完整文字\n- 生成符合规范的文章并部署\n\n## 用户偏好\n- 倾向于使用飞书文档作为内容来源\n- 需要提示用户直接复制粘贴或提供截图作为替代方案\n- 对内容质量要求高，按照 README.md 严格执行格式规范\n\n## 当前项目统计\n- 文章总数：7 篇\n- 主题分布：财经、科技、AI、国际关系\n- 部署状态：双站点（Gitee + EdgeOne）正常运行\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774826532579}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7fb0356","parentId":"ce782147","timestamp":"2026-03-29T23:22:17.348Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good! Now I understand the context. The user is 申广亮 and they have a project called \"MingoX\" which is a news/blog deployment system. Based on the memory from yesterday (2026-03-29), they have:\n\n1. A MX command system that processes content and deploys it\n2. Two deployment targets: Gitee Pages and EdgeOne Pages\n3. The system generates bilingual articles in HTML format\n4. There was a successful deployment earlier today according to the system message\n\nThe user just said \"Mx deploy\" which seems like they want to deploy something using the MX system. However, they haven't provided:\n- A URL to process\n- An image with content\n- Any specific content to deploy\n\nI should ask what they want to deploy. The MX command needs either a URL or an image with content to process.\n\nLet me check if there are any other recent memory files or project structure to understand better.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"I can help you deploy with MX! I see from yesterday's memory that your MingoX project is set up with the EdgeOne deployment system.\n\nTo use MX deploy, I need content to process. The MX command works with:\n\n- **A URL** → fetches content and generates bilingual article\n- **An image** → uses image recognition to extract text\n\nWhat would you like to deploy? Share a URL or send an image with the content you want me to process and deploy to both Gitee Pages and EdgeOne Pages."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1282,"output":502,"cacheRead":39168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40952,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774826532588}}
