{"type":"message","id":"7fc6d106","parentId":"cd299957","timestamp":"2026-03-30T09:15:54.432Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了Gitee的token：76d65c9f51ad0cdfbd24e36ede710bc3\n用户名是：siglea\n\n现在我需要使用Gitee API来创建仓库。Gitee API的创建仓库端点是：\nPOST /api/v5/user/repos\n\n需要的参数：\n- name: 仓库名称\n- description: 仓库描述\n- private: 是否私有（false为公开）\n- auto_init: 是否初始化（false）\n\n我需要使用curl来调用API。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3e0730fd1d76ac06841a39334a51","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -X POST \\\n  -H \"Authorization: token 76d65c9f51ad0cdfbd24e36ede710bc3\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"name\": \"mingox-skill\",\n    \"description\": \"MingoX 自动化发布 Skill - 支持一键发布双语文章到 Gitee + EdgeOne\",\n    \"private\": false,\n    \"auto_init\": false,\n    \"has_issues\": true,\n    \"has_wiki\": true\n  }' \\\n  https://gitee.com/api/v5/user/repos"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":140,"output":361,"cacheRead":125120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125621,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774862142629}}
